data.description: Put this house on your list to see soon!  Lots of designer touches that Chip & Joanna Gaines would approve. Upgrades/Features include: Randy Wise construction, beautiful brick, front & back porches, separate office with new wall unit complete with bookshelves, cabinets, wood shiplap, tv mount and added lights. Split & open floor plan, tankless water heater, WIFI/Alexa enabled light switches, Ring doorbell, Ring security lights, Nest thermostat, chef kitchen: granite countertops, SS appliances, gas stove top, wall oven & microwave, professional fridge/freezer, under & upper cabinet lighting, wooden shelves in pantry with built in coffee/wine bar and oversized island top with overhang for bar stools. Accent wall of faux german smear brick in living room, foyer is lined in wide shiplap... laundry room was expanded and has a laundry sink, counter top, cabinets, closet, and door to garage. Garage has Race Deck floor, electric bike storage lift for 4 bikes, whole house water filtration system, pull down attic stairs, storage area in attic above garage and Kevlar storm shutters for all the windows. Backyard has privacy fence, fire pit, sitting area, room for dogs & kids to play, screened-in porch w/curtains, outside kitchen with natural gas connection, electric smoker, ceiling fan, sprinkler system rust tank added, outdoor lighting, pavers & rocks were added in flower beds and walkways. Located on a cul-de-sac street. Don't let this one pass you by!
